THE MIDDLE OF THE PALACE PLAZA.

167
00:08:51,708 --> 00:08:53,333
- Eslina: OOH AND SOME STALLS!

168
00:08:53,416 --> 00:08:55,208
- THE KEY INGREDIENT HERE
IS PANACHE.

169
00:08:55,291 --> 00:08:57,750
THIS HAS GOT TO BE
THE END-ALL, BE-ALL.

170
00:08:57,833 --> 00:08:59,541
WHAT KIND OF STUFF DO
THEY DO IN ESTABUL?

171
00:08:59,625 --> 00:09:00,750
- WELL, LET ME THINK.

172
00:09:00,833 --> 00:09:03,125
