174
00:09:04,416 --> 00:09:05,541
-FIREWORKS, HUH?

175
00:09:05,625 --> 00:09:07,333
- THEY'RE LIKE GIANT
BLOOMS OF COLORED FLAME

176
00:09:07,416 --> 00:09:08,791
