OF THIS SIZE AND AS YOU SAY,

192
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:41,041
WE DO WANT PANACHE.

193
00:09:41,125 --> 00:09:44,666
- SO I SUPPOSE FIREWORKS
ARE OFF THE TABLE, THEN.

194
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,750
- NO. I THINK I GOT
A WAY AROUND THIS.

195
00:09:46,833 --> 00:09:48,875
