AND SHORT OF IT?

208
00:10:20,625 --> 00:10:22,541
- SURE, FINE.

209
00:10:22,625 --> 00:10:24,541
- ALL SUCH WORRIES SHOULD BE
PUSHED TO THE BACKGROUND

210
00:10:24,625 --> 00:10:27,250
